        <p>This module can be used to login to the site using LinkedIn credentials.</p>
        <p>To make it work:
            <ul>
                <li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/developers/apps">Create LinkedIn app</a></li>
                <li>Add the following <strong>Authorized redirect URLs for your app</strong> in <strong>Auth</strong> section: <strong>{0}</strong></li>
                <li>Add <strong>Sign In with LinkedIn using OpenID Connect</strong> product in <strong>Products</strong> section</li>
                <li>Get generated Client ID & Secret pair from <strong>Auth</strong> section then enter these details in this module settings.</li>
            </ul>            
        </p>]]></string>
